{{Infobox journal | title = ARQ | cover = | discipline = [[Architecture]] | abbreviation =ARQ | editor = Patricio Mardones Hiche | language = Spanish | publisher = [[Pontifical Catholic University of Chile]] | country = Chile | history = 1980–present | frequency = Quarterly or triannual | website = http://www.scielo.cl/revistas/arq/eaboutj.htm | link1 = | link1-name = Online archive | ISSN = 0716-0852 | eISSN = 0717-6996 | OCLC = }} '''''ARQ''''' is a [[scientific journal]] published by the School of Architecture of the [[Pontifical Catholic University of Chile]]. It publishes articles on a wide range of [[architecture]]-related topics, primarily on issues that are relevant to [[Chile]] and [[South America]]. Each issue is centered on one theme.
