{{Italic title}} '''''Empire''''' was a [[South African]] [[magazine]] published every four weeks between December 2007<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bizcommunity.com/Article/196/39/19393.html|title=The dawn of a new media Empire|publisher=Bizcommunity.com|accessdate=20 December 2008}}</ref> and October 2008.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bizcommunity.com/Article/196/39/29278.html|title=Death of a true maverick empire|publisher=Bizcommunity.com|accessdate=20 December 2008}}</ref> It covered media, arts and culture and rapidly established a reputation for controversial articles.
